From 1f6945c1439d8897c7886449fa0c2f0cf1c4be2f Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Viktor AI <viktor@coworker.ai>
Date: Tue, 7 Apr 2026 18:14:36 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] Launch readiness: Remove all promo banners, beta references,
 and fix bugs

Changes:
- Remove expired VOICE_LAUNCH_PROMO banner from homepage and pricing
- Remove Beta Testing banner from homepage
- Remove BETA TESTING badges from About, Contact, Pricing pages
- Enable Stripe checkout (was blocked by beta alert in Billing.tsx)
- Clean up Pricing page: enabled plan buttons, show actual voice pricing
- Remove VOICE_LAUNCH_PROMO constant from constants.ts
- Fix auth security: remove demo login bypass for passwordless accounts
- Fix auth security: remove temp password console.log in forgot-password
- Fix AuthModal: remove debug_temp_pass response handling
- Fix Admin Dashboard: replace fake revenue chart with real user data
- Fix Reseller Dashboard: replace mockEarnings with actual referred user data
- Fix Client Overview: replace hardcoded +15% trend with actual lead count
- Remove debug console.log for referral capture in App.tsx
- Contact page: replace beta testing references with demo/walkthrough CTA
- About page: replace beta CTA with launch-ready signup CTA
- All TypeScript checks pass, production build succeeds
---
